description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a enthusiastic, motivated individuals to join our housekeeping team to help provide and maintain a clean and hygienic environment for all patients, visitors and staff in line with the National Standards of Cleanliness for the University Hospital of North Midlands NHS Trust, County Site Stafford.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The individuals will be adaptable, self-motivated, someone who can work to clearly defined achievable, individual, team and operational goals and any other duties to complete the tasks as required by the Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for 2 vacancies working working on a 2 week rota Saturday and Sunday on 7.30-13.30 &amp; 14.00-20.00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Claire Burns &lt;br /&gt;claire.burns@uhnm.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
